            "title": "Ubuntu 22.04 常用命令",
            "date_published": "2024-03-01T07:09:44.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p>本文记录 Ubuntu 22.04 下一些常用的命令</p>\n<h2 id=\"ssh\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#ssh\">#</a> SSH</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 连接到服务器</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">ssh</span> marshwallen@172.20.20.144\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 从服务器下载文件到指定目录（文件或文件夹）</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">scp</span> root@127.20.36.88:~/test.zip ~/Desktop\n<span class=\"token function\">scp</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-r</span> root@127.20.36.88:~/test ~/Desktop\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 查看历史连接用户</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> /var/log\nlast\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"文件操作\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#文件操作\">#</a> 文件操作</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 压缩</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">tar</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-vcf</span> test.tar ./test\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 解压</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">tar</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-xvf</span> test.tar ./test\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 列出文件夹及大小</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">ls</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-l</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">du</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-h</span> --max-depth<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"环境变量\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#环境变量\">#</a> 环境变量</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 修改</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">vim</span> ~/.bashrc\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 应用修改</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span> ~/.bashrc\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"应用安装-更新\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#应用安装-更新\">#</a> 应用安装、更新</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># apt安装</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> xxx\n<span class=\"token comment\"># apt卸载</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> remove xxx\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> autoremove\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"conda\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#conda\">#</a> Conda</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 创建环境</span>\nconda create <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-n</span> xxx <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">python</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">3.7</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 激活环境</span>\nconda activate xxx\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 查看conda列表</span>\nconda <span class=\"token function\">env</span> list\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 删除环境</span>\nconda <span class=\"token function\">env</span> remove <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-n</span> xxx\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"screen\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#screen\">#</a> Screen</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 创建终端</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">screen</span> 或 <span class=\"token function\">screen</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-S</span> xxx\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 查看终端</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">screen</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-ls</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 恢复终端</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">screen</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-r</span> xxx\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 杀死终端</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">screen</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-S</span> xxx <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-X</span> quit \n<span class=\"token comment\"># 杀死前20个screen</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">screen</span> -ls<span class=\"token operator\">|</span><span class=\"token function\">awk</span> <span class=\"token string\">'NR>=2&amp;&amp;NR&lt;=6&#123;print $1&#125;'</span><span class=\"token operator\">|</span><span class=\"token function\">awk</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&#123;print \"screen -S \"$1\" -X quit\"&#125;'</span><span class=\"token operator\">|</span><span class=\"token function\">sh</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"实用命令\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#实用命令\">#</a> 实用命令</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 把命令行输出保存到txt文件中</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">sh</span> test.sh <span class=\"token operator\">></span> output.txt<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n",
            "tags": [
                "Ubuntu"
            ]
